title: DJ's Mock Draft 2.0
itunes:title: DJ's Mock Draft 2.0
description:
DJ and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. On this special show, DJ gives a breakdown of his full first round 2020 NFL Mock Draft 2.0. Find out which quarterbacks will go in the first round, which position group is the deepest and if there are any surprise players that will sneak into the first round.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
